{"tid":2253632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打讀過美甲課程","createTime":"2020-10-22T09:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T06:41:44.000Z","uid":236411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7079f1161a5530d1b7027c4cd6d227b34edd0f69","tid":2253632,"uid":236411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"畢業冇乜技能 想讀返個美甲<br />\n我見ERB／港專都有啲美甲課程 想知讀完有冇用 因為ERB以外既課程都幾貴<br />\n怕讀完又冇人請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知有冇過來人有經驗"},{"pid":"975ce8646f8352ce57cb5fcd79bd623cc405c34c","tid":2253632,"uid":266668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"香港做美甲周街都係<br />\n調翻轉你係客 都唔會理佢有乜認書點點點，整得靚就得<br />\n自學或者做學徒其實都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d8bde93ef3ea02814120f916cb6b998facc79b","tid":2253632,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"港專有份搞erb課程，但係低B班，比錢出去學好過"},{"pid":"bf7d072f57f1cafd315d29a9fa89ead6cebc24bd","tid":2253632,"uid":100162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f621cb855e7303f8680100a1c9e63c8978a7cd","tid":2253632,"uid":40454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"無讀過, 但整左指甲好多年<br />\n唔同price range 嘅美甲師都有試過<br />\n有讀過嘅係真係唔同(當然唔係個個)<br />\n有讀過美甲最大分別覺得係個底做得真係明顯好好多<br />\n夠薄, 硬淨, 靚shape, 唔易起朴<br />\n識貨嘅客係會試過返唔到轉頭<br />\n我而家嗰個美甲師就係, <br />\n就算收緊average $800 up 一套<br />\n而無學過周街都係嗰啲$200up 就有"},{"pid":"8f58f8293bc8665d276ea59feec32beb9f00f1f0","tid":2253632,"uid":190481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}